The spawn class is the C++ class in the [game code](Coding#game_code "Coding") that defines an entities logic.

Spawn classes use single inheritance with [idEntity](IdEntity_%28class%29 "IdEntity (class)") being the lowest level that can be [spawned](Spawn "Spawn") .

The spawn class is defined by the " **spawnclass** " key in an entities [spawnArgs](SpawnArgs "SpawnArgs") .

